
1) Build x10 stand-alone SUMMA (no BLAS):
> make 

2) Build x10 SUMMA with BLAS 
> make blasxt

3) Build all
> make all

4) Run x10 stand-alone SUMMA

> mpirun -np [num of proc] ./RunSummaXT [matrix size] [panel size]
Default settings: matrix size = 8, panel size = 1

5) Run x10 SUMMA with BLAS

> mpirun -np [num of proc] ./RunSummaXTBlas [matrix size] [panel size]
Default settings: matrix size = 8, panel size = 1


